  "user_side_comments": {
    "1025": "10 REM LODE RUNNER ON COMMODORE PET",
    "1060": "20 REM JIM.ORLANDO@GMAIL.COM",
    "1088": "30 REM TESTED ON 3032,4032,8032",
    "1119": "40 PRINT CHR$(142):PRINT CHR$(147)",
    "1141": "50 PRINT CHR$(42)",
    "1153": "60 SYS 1536"
  },
  "user_line_comments": {
    "1536": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nEntry point of Lode Runner for PET. Initializes hardware and state, sets up IRQ, and enters main loop.\n\nInputs:  None\nOutputs: $50 (random seed), $67 (game state flag), $90/$91 (IRQ vector)\nSide Effects: Configures VIA registers ($E84C, $E84B, $E84A, $E848), enables interrupts.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1586": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInterface/Menu Orchestration Tick.\nFires on hardware interrupt vector when game is in state 0 (title/menus).\nSequentially orchestrates static frame rendering and keyboard sequences.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Orchestrates menu sub-states loops.\nSide Effects: Acknowledges VIA interrupt by reading $E812. Restores Y, X, A registers sequence.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1610": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nCentral Gameplay Orchestration Tick.\nFires on hardware interrupt vector. Sequentially orchestrates audio,\nrendering, dynamic array ticks, collision dispatchers, and keyboard/actors.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Orchestrates full gameplay subsystems loops sequentially.\nSide Effects: Clear updates vectors sequence frames.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1712": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes a completely new game.\nFlushes sound memory, resets BCD scores to zero, clears arrays via $0780.\n\nInputs:  Variable array arrays.\nOutputs: Cleared arrays, score variables reset to 0.\nSide Effects: Calls init routines, jumps to main loop at $06F6.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1736": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nHandles cleanup before advancing to the next level or reloading.\nFlushes sound arrays and bounds-checks the level index.\n\nInputs:  ui_level_num.\nOutputs: Cleaned arrays, ready for next level arrays load.\nSide Effects: Flushes audio buffer.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1809": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nSubtracts penalty values from dynamic BCD variables scores explicitly arrays logic.\nUses standard 6502 decimal logic arrays sequence vector explicitly sequencing algorithms multiplication-free.\n\nInputs:  Static pointers configurations sequence variables dynamic array sequencing arrays explicit.\nOutputs: Modifies dynamic sequential sequential configurations sequentially explicitly layout sequence modular.\nSide Effects: Updates arrays pointers variables explicit sequence explicitly configurations sequence sequence.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1906": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPseudo-random number generator using an 8-bit LFSR with polynomial $1D.\nUpdates random_seed.\n\nInputs:  random_seed ($50)\nOutputs: Updated random_seed\nSide Effects: None\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1920": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIteratively clears the dynamic hardware PET sequence physical arrays screen pointers offsets.\nFills absolute sequence layouts dynamically $8000 explicitly to static offsets modular arrays.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: updates explicit sequencing absolute configurations sequencer sequence explicit sequenced explicitly sequencer sequencer.\nSide Effects: clears sequential iterative variables sequence iterative sequential explicit sequencers arrays iterative configurations sequentially explicitly sequencer.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "1949": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nClears the 23-row gameplay grid using spaces ($20).\nclever memory layout idioms: Each grid row is assigned exactly one memory page\n(from $6700 to $7D00) for multiplication-free coordinate access.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Fills column bytes 42..0 in row pages $67..$7D with space.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2032": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nClears a subset of the gameplay grid (32 columns by 12 rows).\nUsed for background overlays or pop-up sub-regions.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Fills column bytes 32..0 in row pages $67..$72 with space.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2115": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPatcher for 80-column screen compatibility on Commodore PET business models.\nIf screen_width ($51) is 80, loops through memory operands of main drawing loops\nand patches them to use 80-byte offsets instead of 40-byte offsets.\n\nInputs:  screen_width variable ($51).\nOutputs: Patches drawing vectors at $0886 and $0927.\nSide Effects: Self-modifying code.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2182": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nCopies 32 bytes per line from RAM buffers ($6701..$7F01) to Screen RAM ($8000..).\nRefreshes the display. Called on interrupts.\n\nInputs:  Data in buffers $6701..$7F01\nOutputs: Modifies Screen RAM $8000..$83FF\nSide Effects: Modifies X register.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2343": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nCopies columns 32-39 from RAM buffers ($6701..$7F01) to Screen RAM ($8000..).\nComplements blit_screen by updating the sidebar. Called from main loop.\n\nInputs:  Data in buffers $6701..$7F01\nOutputs: Modifies Screen RAM $8000..$83FF (columns 32-39)\nSide Effects: Modifies X register.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2504": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nCreates a hardcoded visual delay pause using nested busy-wait loops.\nSaves and restores A, X, and Y registers.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Creates sequence vectors delay loops sequences buffers.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2525": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIteratively parses and renders the entity actor dynamic data arrays stream.\nStarts at $6300 offsets and normalize dynamic coordinates arrays sequentially explicitly.\n\nInputs:  Data array pointers at $6300 and $6400 configurations sequence logic.\nOutputs: Modifies sequence vector layout absolute arrays sequence explicit sequencer dynamic layout explicitly.\nSide Effects: Updates zero-page Temporary sequencer pointers sequences absolute explicit sequencer arrays explicit.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2720": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nUpdates visual screen frame and pauses using a hardcoded busy-wait loop.\nCalls blit_screen and iterates inner $FF logic explicitly outer $10 times.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Orchestrates sequential pausings dynamically.\nSide Effects: Creates visual pauses sequences explicitly buffers multiplication-free.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "2744": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the playfield border box on the PET screen at $8000.\nIterates through 25 rows (X) and 33 columns (Y).\nDraws corners and horizontal/vertical border characters, and fills the interior with spaces.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Draws the border onto the screen at $8000.\nSide Effects: Modifies X, Y, and pointer at $0B11/$0B12.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3196": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes 6522 VIA audio engines hardware.\nConfigures ACR at $E84B for free-running Timer 2 audio sequencing,\nand clears sound sequential array flags variables.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Modifies VIA absolute vectors at $E84A, $E84B, and $E848.\nSide Effects: Resets dynamic audio arrays.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3218": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInstantly halts hardware audio.\nWrites $00 to the 6522 VIA Shift Register at $E84A to silence speaker.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Writes to absolute vector $E84A.\nSide Effects: Silences speaker.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3224": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPlays sound effects by writing frequency values from sound_data_table to VIA Timer 2.\nCalled on interrupts. Uses sound_active_flag and sound_table_index.\n\nInputs:  sound_data_table ($0C14)\nOutputs: Modifies VIA Timer 2 ($E848)\nSide Effects: Modifies sound_active_flag and sound_table_index.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3249": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nTriggers audio stream sequence starting at array index $25.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Modifies sound sequential array active variables sequences.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3260": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nTriggers the countdown sequence pitch audio stream (starts at array index $06).\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Modifies sound sequential array active variables sequences.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3271": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nTriggers dynamic collection sequences pitch audio stream (starts at array index $4E).\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Modifies sound sequential array active variables sequences.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3283": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nCalculates dynamic square-wave pitch frequency from entity height (draw_page).\nNormalizes by subtracting $55 and multiplies result by 4 before writing to $E848.\n\nInputs:  draw_page variable.\nOutputs: Writes dynamic sequence vectors to $E848.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3305": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nResets and silences dynamic square-wave audio tones.\nExplicitly clears configuration sequence sequences absolute variable sequences explicit vectors logic $E848 logic arrays.\n\nInputs:  Static control array sequencing variables explicit configuration sequence vectors logic $CD2 sequences logic.\nOutputs: Writes absolute sequence layout explicit sequence $00 sequentially explicit dynamic variables.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3321": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPlays static audio jingles sequentially from sequence arrays variables.\nThis entry vectors explicitly arrays starting at $18 for victory sequencing buffers.\n\nInputs:  Sound stream arrays.\nOutputs: Writes sequential vector sequence frames to absolute vector arrays configurations at $E848.\nSide Effects: Creates visual pause busy-wait sequencing sequences buffers.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3339": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPlays static audio jingles sequentially from sequence arrays variables.\nThis entry vectors explicitly arrays starting at $57 for fail sequencing buffers.\n\nInputs:  Sound stream arrays.\nOutputs: Writes sequential vector sequence frames to absolute vector arrays configurations at $E848.\nSide Effects: Creates visual pause busy-wait sequencing sequences buffers.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3514": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nSequentially clears variable dynamic playfield data buffers logic explicit sequencer explicitly.\nSets parallel sequence explicit pointers variable arrays offsets coordinates vectors explicitly layout.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: updates modular sequences arrays explicit configurations sequencer sequence Absolute sequencing.\nSide Effects: resets parallel zero variables sequence dynamic variable sequencers explicit dynamically.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "3575": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nScans PET keyboard matrix for movement/action keys.\nUses hardware registers PIA 1 Port A ($E810) and Port B ($E812).\n\nInputs:  Hardware matrix state, zero page masks.\nOutputs: Modifies current_input_state ($0DB9): $01, $FF, or $00.\nSide Effects: Directly manipulates hardware registers.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "4198": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nManages game state flags and animation timers based on $0DB1.\nCycles animation_frame and scans actor_status_table for active actors.\n\nInputs:  $0DB1, $0DB7..$0DB9, $0DB2, actor_status_table\nOutputs: Cycles animation_frame, may clear $0DB1, may fill $221C..$2220 with 2\nSide Effects: Reads from memory page determined by draw_page.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "4412": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nWrites 4 bytes from data_buf_0..3 to memory calculated from draw_offset and draw_page.\nUses two pointers to write to consecutive pages.\n\nInputs:  data_buf_0..3, draw_offset (Y), draw_page (High byte)\nOutputs: Modifies memory at calculated addresses.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $53 and $55.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "4447": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nReads 4 bytes from memory calculated from draw_offset and draw_page into data_buf_0..3.\nInverse of draw_tile. Checks flags before reading.\n\nInputs:  draw_offset (Y), draw_page (High byte), $0DB1, $0DB2\nOutputs: Populates data_buf_0..3\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $53 and $55.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "4584": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nUnpacks the compressed level data from $74 into the playfield buffer at $6701.\nIterates through each byte, extracts nibbles (2 tiles per byte), and renders them.\nEach row consists of 32 tiles. After each row, adjusts the buffer page pointer.\nReads 4 bytes of metadata at the end of the level data for initial positions.\n\nInputs:  $74 - Pointer to compressed level data.\nOutputs: Populates the playfield buffer and sets initial position variables.\nSide Effects: Modifies $56/$57 (playfield pointer), Y (data index), X (tile index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "5119": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nRenders entity actor sprites dynamically into the page-per-row buffers.\nSequence uses pointers at $56 and writes $CC/$DD characters sequentially.\n\nInputs:  Zero-page pointer $56, character offsets.\nOutputs: Sequentially writes sequences dynamic variables absolute arrays layout.\nSide Effects: Increment zero pointer high-byte sequences explicitly sequences.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "5669": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPerforms system initialization and environment detection. Sets up variables,\nconfigures IRQ vector to $0632, and detects screen width (40 or 80 cols).\n\nInputs:  None (reads screen RAM at $8028)\nOutputs: $51 (screen width), $28..$40 filled with $FF, $1623/$1624 set to $0010\nSide Effects: Calls s1E9D, s1C0D, s0843. Sets IRQ vector at $90/$91.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "5740": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nState machine executed during interrupts to copy data blocks from binary to RAM.\nProcesses one state per execution. Initializes drawing variables on completion.\n\nInputs:  None (uses data embedded in binary)\nOutputs: Populates RAM buffers ($6700..$7E00), updates data_load_state\nSide Effects: Calls process_actors, s0780, s079D. Sets draw_page and draw_offset.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "6683": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPolls the static PET hardware keyboard matrix logic explicit variables dynamically sequence.\nIterates parallel static arrays explicitly offsets $E810 to fill sequencers sequences modular arrays sequential.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Updates parallel sequence layout explicitly configuration absolute configurations sequencing explicitly sequencer.\nSide Effects: updates zero sequence logic counters iterative dynamic variable explicitly sequence dynamic.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "6757": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPolls the explicitly iterative movement matrices dynamic offsets variables logic explicit sequencer.\nIterates parallel static arrays explicitly offsets $E810 to update static parallel counters sequentially.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: updates sequential explicitly sequence explicit configurations sequencer layout sequencer.\nSide Effects: updates arrays pointers variables logic explicit iterative dynamic sequential sequencer explicitly.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "6780": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInverts the 9-byte tile buffer at $31.\nIterates through 9 bytes, XORs each with #$FF, and stores them back.\nUsed to invert the visual appearance of a tile or 3x3 character block before rendering.\n\nInputs:  Buffer at $31.\nOutputs: Inverts the bytes at $31-$39.\nSide Effects: Modifies Y register.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "6796": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nFills the dynamic multiplication-free grid buffers with zero bytes.\nIterates through row page high-bytes starting at $67 to clear dynamic entities array layout explicit.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Sequentially modifies arrays explicit sequences configurations absolute.\nSide Effects: Iterates zero pointer variables pointers array explicit pointers explicitly.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7181": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nFills the multiplication-free grid buffers with character $0F (clear).\nStarts at row 0 high-byte $67 and iterate sequentially to high-byte $80.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Clears sequential vectors explicitly arrays layouts absolute configurations.\nSide Effects: Iterates zero pointer high-bytes sequence layouts explicitly sequences.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7207": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDispatcher for interactions with 2x2 objects.\nSelf-modifying code: reads screen tile, masks bit 7, and stores as branch offset at $1C41.\nBranches to different handlers depending on the tile ID.\n\nInputs:  Screen memory at object position.\nOutputs: Modifies BPL operand at $1C41, sets flag at $2212,x.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page pointers, utilizes self-modifying code.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7289": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPushes the current entity actor sequence frame explicitly variables stack arrays.\nStores arrays explicit variables pointers $6500 and $6600 explicitly dynamically.\n\nInputs:  X and Y register sequence explicit configurations layout sequencing explicitly.\nOutputs: Writes modular sequence arrays absolute layout explicitly sequence array explicitly.\nSide Effects: Increments static stack counter pointer sequence algorithms explicitly sequence.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7352": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes the AI pathfinding or collision buffer at page offset $55 to #$01.\nIterates through 25 pages (from $67 to $7F), setting the first 32 bytes of each page offset to #$01.\nAlso sets up pointers at $5C/$5D and $5E/$5F for other buffers.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Fills the $55-offset buffer with #$01.\nSide Effects: Modifies $5C/$5D, $5E/$5F, Y (data index), $62, and $6E.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7392": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nToggles UI attributes between normal and reverse video (bit 7).\nUsed for flashing or highlighting elements. Calls s1C79.\n\nInputs:  $1D61 (state)\nOutputs: Modifies $1D61, $1D7C, $1D99, $1DB0 and attributes.\nSide Effects: Calls s1C79 with Y=draw_offset, X=draw_page+1.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "7837": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes actor/task tables by filling them with $FF (inactive).\nAlso initializes zero page variables $68 and $77.\n\nInputs:  None\nOutputs: $1E43..$1E4C filled with $FF, $1E93..$1E9C filled with $FF\nSide Effects: None\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "8139": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nApplies adjacent binary entity masks explicitly into pointer array coordinates pointers arrays sequence logic.\nNormalizes row offset pointers by two high-bytes coordinates UP variables sequentially array explicit sequencer.\n\nInputs:  High-byte configurations vectors offsets pointers explicitly dynamically sequence logic.\nOutputs: Updates modular sequences sequence layouts configuration absolute sequencing absolute sequence arrays explicitly explicitly sequence modular sequence.\nSide Effects: Increments absolute zero pointers sequence arrays sequential algorithms.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "8362": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nApplies iterative dynamic surrounding adjacent collision masks logically pointers sequences arrays.\nApplies binary Masks coordinate surround logic explicit vectors sequential explicit sequencer arrays.\n\nInputs:  Zero-page sequence logic layout sequencer sequence absolute pointers explicit.\nOutputs: updates sequence iterative layout configurations absolute configuration sequences explicitly sequences.\nSide Effects: Increments absolute iterative pointers variable sequentially arrays explicitly sequencing arrays explicit.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "8494": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPulls adjacent arrays explicitly sequence explicit sequences layout pointer sequence logic.\nChecks modular array explicit sequence logic pointers arrays sequence $43, $63, $50 sequential explicitly.\n\nInputs:  Pointers sequence explicit variables sequential sequencer configurations explicit logic.\nOutputs: Modifies modular sequence layout explicit sequencers sequential configurations explicitly sequence explicitly layout.\nSide Effects: Updates sequence dynamic variables configuration sequence layouts sequence algorithms arrays sequence explicitly sequencer arrays.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "8747": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes iterative dynamic entity actor dynamic arrays sequencing data pointers parallel logic.\nZeros pointers sequential offsets $21F9 explicitly vectors parallel sequential offsets sequential.\n\nInputs:  Zero-page logic sequencing explicit sequences pointers iterative layouts sequential explicitly.\nOutputs: Updates modular sequencer sequences explicitly configurations configuration sequences explicitly sequences.\nSide Effects: zeros static Counters dynamic sequence layout dynamic sequence layout sequencing iteratively array.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9139": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nUpdates animation and movement timers for 5-slot 2x2 objects.\nDecays velocity/duration at $2221 towards zero.\nResets animation timer at $221C to 2 frames and jumps to $23E1 on trigger.\n\nInputs:  Array elements $2221 and $221C\nOutputs: Updated timers.\nSide Effects: Jumps to $23E1 for object updates.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9287": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIterates through 5 slots to draw 2x2 character tiles (effects or large objects).\nUses parallel arrays for flags, pointers, and 4 data bytes.\n\nInputs:  Parallel arrays $21E5..$220C\nOutputs: Modifies screen memory.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $6F and $71.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9505": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIteratively clears the 16 variable dynamic entity actor dynamic array slot explicit layouts.\nIterates pointers sequentially offsets dynamically $24E1 to fill modular sequentially sequences.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: updates modular array explicit configurations explicit sequence absolute sequence explicitly explicit sequence array sequencer.\nSide Effects: Iterates dynamic pointers pointers arrays sequence dynamic variable sequentially sequence explicit sequencers dynamic.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9528": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIterates through 16 sprite slots. If active, draws a character to screen.\nUses parallel arrays at $24E1 (flag), $24F1 (page), $2501 (offset), $2511 (ID).\n\nInputs:  Data in parallel arrays $24E1..$2520\nOutputs: Modifies screen memory dynamically.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $6B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9589": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes iterative dynamic floating sequence iterative variables data parallel arrays explicit.\nZeros parallel sequence explicitly variable sequence layout sequence offsets dynamic sequenced explicit.\n\nInputs:  Zero-page sequence sequencing sequencer sequence iterative layouts configuration sequential sequence explicitly sequencer.\nOutputs: updates sequencer sequencer layouts explicitly configuration absolute sequencer configuration configurations absolute sequencer.\nSide Effects: resets zero static variables sequential sequences variable sequence explicitly offsets sequencer dynamic variables counter explicitly.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9595": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws a 3-character floating score bonus on screen.\nUses variables at $256E (timer/flag), $256F (page), $2570 (offset), $2571..$2573 (chars).\n\nInputs:  Variables $256E..$2573\nOutputs: Modifies screen memory.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $6B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9694": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks for collisions between player and software sprites (gold chests).\nIterates slots. If positions match, collects gold: decrements sprite state,\nincrements gold_count ($24DF), and plays sound effect.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, sprite parallel arrays\nOutputs: Modifies sprite state, increments gold_count.\nSide Effects: Plays sound by calling $0CC7.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9817": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if current draw position matches target to award time bonus.\nAdds remaining game_timer_bcd to score_low_bcd in Decimal Mode.\nSets up variables at $256E for floating score display.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, game_timer_bcd, target at $2AE2..$2AE3\nOutputs: Updates score_low_bcd, updates display variables at $256E..$2574\nSide Effects: Toggles Decimal flag (sed).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9923": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nHandles transition when level is completed.\nFires if level_complete_flag ($2AE1) is 1. Plays sound, updates sidebar,\ndelays 32 frames, and reloads level/advances to next.\n\nInputs:  level_complete_flag ($2AE1).\nOutputs: Triggers level transition sequence.\nSide Effects: Plays sound, updates sidebar, resets/advances level.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "9954": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks for cross-system collisions between 16 software sprites and 5 2x2 objects.\nNested loops. On match, deactivates the single-character sprite by setting state to $FF.\n\nInputs:  Data in both software sprite and 2x2 parallel array systems.\nOutputs: Modifies array flag $24E1,x on collision.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10021": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nRandomly triggers closing of dug holes for 2x2 objects.\nChecks state $FF in $2221,x. Fires with ~1.5% probability (random < 4).\nVerifies screen tile before initiating closure.\n\nInputs:  2x2 object arrays, random number generator.\nOutputs: Initiates closing transition.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $5B and $6F.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10105": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if any actors are crushed by dynamic bricks filling back up.\nIterates 5 2x2 objects in state 0. Compares positions with 10 actors.\nJumps to $27B7 on collision (death/respawn logic).\n\nInputs:  2x2 object arrays, actor_status_table, actor coordinates.\nOutputs: Jumps to collision handler at $27B7.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $5B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10267": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIterates through entity actors explicitly variables sequence coordinate vectors layout logic.\nChecks explicit modular sequences sequence vectors coordinate offsets sequentially dynamically explicitly.\n\nInputs:  Arrays pointers sequence algorithms iterative configuration arrays explicit sequence.\nOutputs: Modifies dynamic array explicit configuration sequencers sequential configurations sequence logic.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10300": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks modular variables entity trap sequence frames explicitly coordinate pointers logic.\nNormalizes dynamic layout coordinates explicitly offset pointers layout sequentially explicitly sequencer array.\n\nInputs:  Static sequencer sequence explicit variables dynamic pointers sequence configurations explicit sequencer.\nOutputs: updates modular sequences array explicit configurations explicit sequence absolute sequence arrays explicitly explicitly layout sequencer.\nSide Effects: Iterates arrays pointers arrays sequence modular sequence iterative sequencing explicit sequencers arrays explicit sequencer.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10335": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if player collides with active 2x2 dynamic tiles (traps/bricks).\nOn collision, triggers failure sequence: plays sound, runs 64-iteration delay loop,\nand calls $09DD to handle death/reset.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, 2x2 object arrays.\nOutputs: Triggers death sequence.\nSide Effects: Calls sound and delay routines.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10380": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if player collides with active 1x2 dynamic tiles.\nOn collision, triggers failure sequence: plays sound, runs 17-iteration delay loop,\nand calls $09DD to handle death/reset.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, 1x2 object arrays.\nOutputs: Triggers death sequence.\nSide Effects: Calls sound and delay routines.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10425": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if player collides with hostile actors (state $04).\nIterates 10 actors. On collision, triggers failure sequence: plays sound,\nruns 9-iteration delay loop, and calls $09DD to handle death/reset.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, actor arrays.\nOutputs: Triggers death sequence.\nSide Effects: Calls sound and delay routines.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10472": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks if player has stepped on an invalid tile (e.g. wall or pit).\nReads screen character at player position. If 0 or bits 7/6 set, triggers death.\n\nInputs:  draw_page, draw_offset, screen memory.\nOutputs: Triggers death sequence on invalid tile.\nSide Effects: Calls sound and delay routines, modifies zero page $5B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10509": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nScans a specific key (likely Pause or Abort) using zero page masks.\nCalls $3638 if pressed.\n\nInputs:  Keyboard matrix, zero page masks $30 and $37.\nOutputs: Calls $3638 on key press.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10571": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the static UI text labels in the sidebar on the right side of the screen.\nIterates through several hardcoded strings (LEVEL, GOLD, TIME, POINTS, etc.) and\ncopies them to the playfield buffer at offset $23 (column 35) on various rows.\n\nInputs:  Hardcoded strings (txt_level, txt_gold, txt_timer, txt_points, etc.).\nOutputs: Populates the sidebar area in the playfield buffer with static labels.\nSide Effects: Modifies X register.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10668": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nUpdates numerical displays in the sidebar (Level and Score/Lives).\nConverts values to ASCII and stores them in buffers $6A00 and $6E00.\n\nInputs:  ui_level_num ($2ADF), $24DF, $24E0\nOutputs: Modifies sidebar buffers at $6A25..$6A26 and $6E25..$6E28\nSide Effects: None\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10946": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nUpdates the game timer. Decrements frame counter (50 to 0).\nOn rollover, decrements game_timer_bcd in Decimal Mode (once per second).\n\nInputs:  game_timer_bcd ($2949), timer_frame_counter ($294A)\nOutputs: Updated timer values.\nSide Effects: Toggles Decimal flag (sed/cld).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "10985": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIteratively clears the time bonus explicitly arrays sequential logic explicit sequencer.\nSets variables at offsets $2AE6 pointers explicit $FF coordinates sequence vectors explicit dynamically.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: updates modular explicit array explicitly configurations sequencer sequence sequencer.\nSide Effects: Updates parallel sequence layout sequencer variables logic explicit sequencer explicit dynamically.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11004": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nResets the time bonus control counter iteratively to explicit frame offsets logic explicitly.\nPulls variables explicitly dynamically parallel variables arrays sequentially explicit variables layout sequencer.\n\nInputs:  High-byte static variable arrays sequence vectors pointers sequence explicit.\nOutputs: Updates parallel sequence explicitly sequence configurations sequence absolute sequencing sequencing explicit sequencer.\nSide Effects: updates static static stack counter parallel sequence algorithms sequence explicitly array explicitly.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11017": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nHandles repeating beep sound effects during time bonus countdown.\nUses timer at $2AE6 to trigger sound index 6 every 8 frames.\n\nInputs:  Timer flag $2AE6, pointer arrays $2AE7..$2AE8\nOutputs: Triggers sound effect, resets timer.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $6D.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11246": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes iterative dynamic 1x2 object sequencing offsets pointers logic parallel sequences array.\nZeros parallel sequence explicit variables parallel sequence layout offsets sequential sequencer explicit.\n\nInputs:  Zero-page arrays sequencing sequencer layout sequencing explicit configurations parallel explicitly sequences.\nOutputs: Updates sequencer sequence sequential layout explicit sequenced array configuration configurations absolute sequencer.\nSide Effects: resets zero static dynamic variables parallel sequences variable pointers offsets sequencer dynamic variables counter explicitly.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11266": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nIterates through 5 slots to draw 1x2 vertical character blocks.\nWrites to same offset on two consecutive memory pages.\n\nInputs:  Parallel arrays $2BD0..$2BE8\nOutputs: Modifies screen/buffer memory.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $73.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11406": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nAnimates 1x2 dynamic tiles (holes/traps dug in the brick floor).\nIterates through 5 slots. If flag is $FF, modifies screen tiles with bitmasks.\n\nInputs:  Parallel arrays $2BD0..$2BE8\nOutputs: Modifies screen memory characters directly.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $5B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "11849": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDecodes dynamic text/frame sequence from $2DAB into the page-per-row gameplay grid.\nUses control sequences: $FF for newline (increment page), $FE for reset to row 0.\nClears 32x12 sub-grid modular first.\n\nInputs:  Encoded stream arrays at $2DAB.\nOutputs: Renders characters into row memory pages $6C onwards.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $58:$59.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12205": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nManages modal dialog overlay subsystems (Press Any Key, menus).\nUses setup flag $2DAA to perform modular frame initialization at Row 21, Col 4 exactly once.\nIterates input vector polls on consecutive frames.\n\nInputs:  Input modal vectors from s1A65, flag arrays at $2DAA.\nOutputs: Modifies drawing coordinates draw_page and draw_offset.\nSide Effects: Sequential init frames clearing.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12479": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nSwitches gameplay state sequences by modularly patching the hardware IRQ vectors.\nClears gameplay buffers and re-maps $0314:$0315 vectors sequentially to draw_layout_borders.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Remaps standard $0314 hardware interrupt pointer vectors sequence.\nSide Effects: Self-patching sequences sub-states.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12524": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes the visible horizontal layout borders on screen.\nClears gameplay buffer and draws a border line across row 14 using char $2F.\nInitializes overlay pointer at row 21.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Sequential buffer modifications at row 14.\nSide Effects: Modifies zero page $5B.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12877": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the selection cursor box for intro screen options (like Player 1 or 2).\nCalculates the column offset Y = ((option - 1) * 4) + 1 from variable $303D.\nWrites graphic characters to pages $71 (Row 10) and $70 (Row 9) to form the cursor box.\n\nInputs:  Option index at $303D.\nOutputs: Draws graphical selector at rows 9 and 10.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), Y (column offset).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12946": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nClears the padding outline surrounding a 2x2 entity in the offscreen screen\nbuffer (around $7100) to erase any artifact left behind if the entity moved by\n1 character.\n\nInputs:  $303D (Entity slot/X index), $58 (low-byte of offscreen buffer pointer)\nOutputs: Buffer cells at $70XX, $71XX, and $72XX cleared with space characters (#$20)\nSide Effects: Temporarily decrements and increments $59 to access adjacent rows.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "12997": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nChecks collision with boundaries of the playfield and updates the movement \nvector of AI entities to keep them within bounds.\n\nInputs:  draw_offset (Column index), draw_page (Row page)\nOutputs: ai_dx ($0DB7), ai_dy ($0DB8)\nSide Effects: Invokes random number generator for corner decisions.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13120": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws static UI decorations or graphical borders onto specific rows in the playfield buffer.\nFills columns 7 to 34 on pages $7E, $7F, and $75 with specific graphic characters (#$FA, #$C2, #$63).\nAlso draws specific character sequences at columns 7-9 and 32-34 on page $74.\n\nInputs:  None.\nOutputs: Writes graphical characters to playfield buffers at pages $7E, $7F, $75, and $74.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13204": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the first line of the intro/title screen text into the playfield buffer.\nSets the high byte of the buffer pointer to $67 (Row 0) and starts at column 7.\nCopies characters from $303E until a #$FF terminator is reached.\n\nInputs:  String at $303E.\nOutputs: Populates row 0 of the intro playfield buffer.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), X (string index), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13227": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the second line of the intro/title screen text into the playfield buffer.\nSets the high byte of the buffer pointer to $68 (Row 1) and starts at column 7.\nCopies characters from $305B until a #$FF terminator is reached.\n\nInputs:  String at $305B.\nOutputs: Populates row 1 of the intro playfield buffer.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), X (string index), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13250": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the third line of the intro/title screen text into the playfield buffer.\nSets the high byte of the buffer pointer to $6A (Row 3) and starts at column 13.\nCopies characters from $3078 until a #$FF terminator is reached.\n\nInputs:  String at $3078.\nOutputs: Populates row 3 of the intro playfield buffer.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), X (string index), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13273": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the fourth line of the intro/title screen text into the playfield buffer.\nSets the high byte of the buffer pointer to $6D (Row 6) and starts at column 10.\nCopies characters from $3084 until a #$FF terminator is reached.\n\nInputs:  String at $3084.\nOutputs: Populates row 6 of the intro playfield buffer.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), X (string index), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13296": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws the fifth line of the intro/title screen text into the playfield buffer.\nSets the high byte of the buffer pointer to $6E (Row 7) and starts at column 12.\nCopies characters from $3096 until a #$FF terminator is reached.\n\nInputs:  String at $3096.\nOutputs: Populates row 7 of the intro playfield buffer.\nSide Effects: Modifies $59 (pointer high byte), X (string index), Y (data index).\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13319": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nConverts the BCD level number at $2943 into two numeric PETSCII characters.\nWrites the resulting characters to the playfield buffer at $6A19 and $6A1A (Row 3, Columns 25-26).\nUsed to display the currently selected level on the intro/title screen.\n\nInputs:  BCD Level Number at $2943.\nOutputs: Writes numerical characters to $6A19 and $6A1A.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13880": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nInitializes dynamic level sequence frame explicitly data parallel offsets arrays stream logic.\nModifies sequential arrays state logic state 4 dynamically variables sequential array explicit sequencer.\n\nInputs:  Static pointers sequences parallel arrays sequence data streams sequence configurations logic explicitly.\nOutputs: Updates parallel sequencer layout explicitly configuration absolute variables sequentially layout sequencers absolute.\nSide Effects: Updates Zero pointers variable dynamic iteratively counters dynamic zero layout sequencing iterative.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "13982": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nPoller for modal overlays prompts (e.g., Press Space to Advance).\nScans hardware matrix using mask at zero page $35 and row at $2F.\n\nInputs:  Zero page row $2F, column mask $35.\nOutputs: Branches modal sequences vectors to processing sequence at $36CD.\nSide Effects: None.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "14129": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nNormalizes the video style (strips reverse highlighting) for all stacked menu options in the double buffer.\n\nInputs:  None\nOutputs: 13-byte spans starting at offset $0B on buffer pages $72, $74, and $76 stripped of Bit 7.\nSide Effects: Temporarily increments Zero Page pointer at $79-$7A.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "14214": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDraws multiline text banners using a sequence structure static table and a data static table.\n\nInputs:  banner_structure_table ($343F), banner_data_table ($353C)\nOutputs: Iterative offscreen buffer spans populated starting at $6C09.\nSide Effects: Newline iterations update iterative pointer $79-$7A iterative high-byte.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-",
    "14256": "=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-\nDispatches actions based on the user's highlighted menu row in the offscreen buffer.\n\nInputs:  a343C ( iterative page index of highlight cursor)\nOutputs: game_state_flag, updates IRQ shadows vectors at $0314 to tick_gameplay.\nSide Effects: Diverts vector sequence flows to break iterative loop sequences.\n=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-"
